comparison.sql_pred:
WITH agn_objects AS
  (SELECT oid
   FROM probability
   WHERE class_name = 'AGN'
     AND ranking = 1
     AND classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'),
     r_band_variability AS
  (SELECT oid
   FROM feature
   WHERE fid = 2
     AND name IN ('Amplitude',
                  'ExcessVar',
                  'Std')
     AND value IS NOT NULL
     AND oid IN
       (SELECT oid
        FROM agn_objects)),
     g_band_no_variability AS
  (SELECT oid
   FROM feature
   WHERE fid = 1
     AND name IN ('Amplitude',
                  'ExcessVar',
                  'Std',
                  'n_det')
     AND (value IS NULL
          OR value = 0)
     AND oid IN
       (SELECT oid
        FROM agn_objects)),
     combined_features AS
  (SELECT oid,
          name,
          value
   FROM feature
   WHERE oid IN
       (SELECT oid
        FROM r_band_variability)
     OR oid IN
       (SELECT oid
        FROM g_band_no_variability)),
     filtered_oids AS
  (SELECT oid
   FROM combined_features
   GROUP BY oid
   HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT name) = 2)
SELECT o.*,
       f.name,
       f.value
FROM OBJECT o
JOIN combined_features f ON o.oid = f.oid
WHERE o.oid IN
    (SELECT oid
     FROM filtered_oids)
ORDER BY o.oid,
         f.value ASC;

SELECT *

SELECT
  feature.oid, feature.value, feature.name, feature.fid, feature.version, obj_oids.meanra, obj_oids.meandec, obj_oids.ndet

  (
SELECT
    object.oid, object.meanra, object.meandec, object.ndet
FROM
    object INNER JOIN
    probability
    ON object.oid = probability.oid
WHERE
    probability.classifier_name='lc_classifier'
    AND probability.class_name='AGN'
    AND probability.probability > 0.6
    AND object.deltajd > 365
    AND object.ndet > 20
) as obj_oids
    INNER JOIN
    feature ON feature.oid = obj_oids.oid
WHERE
  feature.name = 'Amplitude'
  AND feature.value > 1
  AND feature.fid = 1
) as sq1
UNION
SELECT *
FROM (
SELECT
  feature.oid, feature.value, feature.name, feature.fid, feature.version, obj_oids.meanra, obj_oids.meandec, obj_oids.ndet
FROM
  (
SELECT
    object.oid, object.meanra, object.meandec, object.ndet
FROM
    object INNER JOIN
    probability
    ON object.oid = probability.oid
WHERE
    probability.classifier_name='lc_classifier'
    AND probability.class_name='AGN'
    AND probability.probability > 0.6
    AND object.deltajd > 365
    AND object.ndet > 20
) as obj_oids
    INNER JOIN
    feature ON feature.oid = obj_oids.oid
WHERE
  feature.name = 'Amplitude'
  AND feature.value > 0.5
  AND feature.fid = 2
) as sq2
ORDER BY oid
) AS sq
  INNER JOIN magstat
  ON sq.oid = magstat.oid
WHERE
  sq.oid in (
SELECT oid

SELECT

FROM
  (
SELECT
    object.oid, object.meanra, object.meandec, object.ndet
FROM
    object INNER JOIN

WHERE
    probability.classifier_name='lc_classifier'
    AND probability.class_name='AGN'
    AND probability.probability > 0.6
    AND object.deltajd > 365
    AND object.ndet > 20
) as obj_oids
    INNER JOIN
    feature ON feature.oid = obj_oids.oid
WHERE
  feature.name = 'Amplitude'
  AND feature.value > 1
  AND feature.fid = 1
) as sq1
INTERSECT
SELECT oid
FROM (
SELECT
  feature.oid, feature.value, feature.name, feature.fid, feature.version, obj_oids.meanra, obj_oids.meandec, obj_oids.ndet
FROM
  (
SELECT
    object.oid, object.meanra, object.meandec, object.ndet

WHERE

WITH probability_subquery AS
  (SELECT oid
   FROM probability
   WHERE class_name = 'AGN'
     AND probability > 0.6
     AND ranking = 1
     AND classifier_name = 'lc_classifier'),
     detection_g AS
  (SELECT oid,
          MAX(magpsf_corr) - MIN(magpsf_corr) AS delta_mag_g
   FROM detection
   WHERE fid = 1
   GROUP BY oid
   HAVING MAX(magpsf_corr) - MIN(magpsf_corr) > 1),
     detection_r AS
  (SELECT oid,
          MAX(magpsf_corr) - MIN(magpsf_corr) AS delta_mag_r
   FROM detection
   WHERE fid = 2
   GROUP BY oid
   HAVING MAX(magpsf_corr) - MIN(magpsf_corr) > 0.5),
     detection_count AS
  (SELECT oid,
          fid,
          COUNT(*) AS count_detections
   FROM detection
   GROUP BY oid,
            fid
   HAVING COUNT(*) >= 20),
     object_filtered AS
  (SELECT o.oid,
          o.meanra,
          o.meandec,
          o.ndet,
          o.deltajd
   FROM OBJECT o
   INNER JOIN probability_subquery p ON o.oid = p.oid
   WHERE o.deltajd >= 365),
     feature_filtered AS
  (SELECT f.oid,
          f.name,
          f.value,
          f.version,
          f.fid AS feature_fid
   FROM feature f
   INNER JOIN probability_subquery p ON f.oid = p.oid)
SELECT o.oid,
       f.name,
       f.value,
       f.version,
       f.feature_fid,
       o.meanra,
       o.meandec,
       o.ndet,
       dg.delta_mag_g,
       dr.delta_mag_r
FROM object_filtered o
INNER JOIN feature_filtered f ON o.oid = f.oid
INNER JOIN detection_g dg ON o.oid = dg.oid
INNER JOIN detection_r dr ON o.oid = dr.oid
INNER JOIN detection_count dc ON o.oid = dc.oid
ORDER BY o.oid;
